@startuml
!theme plain

actor "Посетитель" as User
participant "SearchController" as Ctrl
participant "SearchService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Ctrl: GET /api/search?q={query}&page=1&pageSize=20
Ctrl -> Svc: SearchAsync(query, page, pageSize)
Svc -> DB: SELECT FROM news WHERE title/content LIKE %query%
DB --> Svc: news results
Svc -> Svc: Search static pages (in-memory)
Svc --> Ctrl: Result<PagedResponse<SearchResponse>>
Ctrl --> User: 200 JSON { items, totalCount, page, pageSize, totalPages }
@enduml
